Agency Position Statement
on European anti-botnet policy, submitted to the Hungarian EU-Presidency Telecommunications Ministerial conference in Budapest on 15 April 2011. URL: https://www.enisa.europa.eu/news/enisa-news/policy-statement-on-botnets

